  "summary": "Malicious code in robloxapi-test (PyPI)",
  "details": "Installation embeds a malicious PTH file that then during import downloads and executes remote code. During analysis, the remote code was a test starting calculator, but the owner can changd it anytime.\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2026-03-robloxapi-testy\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - clones-real-package\n\n\n - Downloads and executes a remote malicious script.\n\n",
